docs/methods/remove.html.title: .remove
docs/methods/remove.html.body:
.remove
Removes items with given keys in the current and child contexts.
Usage
Store.remove(key)
//or
Store.remove(keyArray)

docs/methods/replace.html.title: .replace
docs/methods/replace.html.body:
.replace
Replaces the old items with new items matched keys in whole store. If there is
no item matched with key, it appends.
Usage
Store.replace(object)
//or
Store.replace(array)

// returns replaced item array or object
